415
00:38:22,903 --> 00:38:24,343
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat ceroboh.</font>

416
00:38:25,843 --> 00:38:27,643
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa kau tidak beritahu kami?</font>

417
00:38:30,073 --> 00:38:32,143
