438
00:40:09,873 --> 00:40:11,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah, hentikan.</font>

439
00:40:11,213 --> 00:40:14,353
<font color=#FFFF00>Pelayan mengira kami memesan,</font>

440
00:40:14,453 --> 00:40:17,453
