493
00:44:00,943 --> 00:44:03,073
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo? Halo?</font>

494
00:44:04,883 --> 00:44:07,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan beritahu apa yang kau cemaskan.</font>

495
00:44:09,013 --> 00:44:10,783
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, pelaksana...</font>

496
00:44:11,653 --> 00:44:14,393
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan membunuh pemilik rumah ini.</font>

497
00:44:16,853 --> 00:44:19,193
