513
00:44:58,563 --> 00:45:01,673
<font color=#FFFF00>dan bilang akan membunuh pendosa di rumah itu.</font>

514
00:45:02,133 --> 00:45:03,703
<font color=#FFFF00>Pendosa?</font>

515
