535
00:45:57,163 --> 00:45:58,163
<font color=#FFFF00>Betul.</font>

536
00:45:59,493 --> 00:46:01,263
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi keserakahan di antara mereka.</font>

537
00:46:02,963 --> 00:46:05,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu yang mereka maksudkan
